{"about_the_game":"<strong>Astrumis - Survive Together</strong> is an <u>exclusively co-op</u> horror game designed for two players. One player controls a survivor on an abandoned spaceship and the other the ship itself. They must work together to navigate the ship, solve puzzles &amp; minigames and survive against the mysterious monster. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/survivorgameplay.gif?t=1739777252\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE SURVIVOR</h2>Play as <strong>the survivor - John Kowalski</strong>. Walk around the ship and come face to face with the invisible monster. Heed instructions from the other player on how to avoid it and stay alive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/mcgameplay.gif?t=1739777252\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MISSION CONTROL</h2>Play as <strong>mission control - Yang Sungbin</strong>. Even though the monster is invisible to the naked eye, security cameras can reveal his location. Take control of them to help the other player navigate the spaceship safely.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/minigamesGIF.gif?t=1739777252\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COOP CHALLENGES</h2>Solve a variety of cooperative minigames. None can be completed alone, each requires you to work together with the other player.<br><br><br><br><i>Inspired by games like <strong>A Way Out</strong> and <strong>Keep Talking and Nobody Explodes</strong> - this project is made by a single developer in Unreal Engine 5, so please be patient, any updates will take time.</i>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2924860?t=1739777252","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739777252","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co